title: Wall Street Breakfast: The Week Ahead
author: Seeking Alpha
dc:creator: Seeking Alpha
description: Analysts are cautiously optimistic over upcoming earnings reports from tech giants Apple (AAPL) and Amazon (AMZN). Intel (INTC) is setting its self-driving subsidiary Mobileye (MBLY) free in a major IPO offering. And, renewable energy could account for 35% of power generation in the U.S. by 2030… how will big oil companies fair?
